      "role": "user",
      "content": "i feel like im just spinning my wheels. every time i think i finally fixed something—my job, my head, my relationship—it just falls apart again. it's like i'm stuck in this loop of failing over and over. i'm just so tired of trying to fix things that are fundamentally broken.",
